{"title":"Mavic Deemax Helmet Doesn’t Come in Yellow, Unless You Count the MIPS Liner","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-deemax-helmet-mips/","date":1699911805000,"content":"<p><img width=\"5568\" height=\"3712\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48.png\" alt=\"Mavic Deemax helmet with MIPS\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48.png 5568w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-297x198.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-800x533.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-120x80.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-768x512.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-2048x1365.png 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SV-202211-Deemax-helmet-by-Keno-Derleyn-48-720x480.png 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Just weeks after announcing the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/yellow-mavic-deemax-dh-wheels-are-back-as-25th-anniversary-of-an-unbreakable-legend/\" target=\"_blank\">return of the legendary Deemax yellow wheels</a>, Mavic has another product under the same name. This time, Mavic is offering a new helmet with the integrated protection of MIPS. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"781\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9-800x781.jpeg\" alt=\"Mavic Deemax helmet with MIPS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9-800x781.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9-297x290.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9-120x117.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9-768x749.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips9.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed for protection on the rugged trails worthy of the Deemax name, the 2024 version of the Deemax MIPS helmet offers extended coverage similar to many enduro half shells. Inside, you’ll find integrated MIPS technology with the telltale yellow liner. Out front, a multi position adjustable visor allows for goggles to be stored underneath. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the more unique features of the helmet is the Mavic Autofit strap system. This is a system Mavic has used previously that utilizes tubular webbing for the ear cradles, which allows the chin strap to rotate around the ear cradle for perfect position of both. The helmet also uses their Ergo Hold SL-3 position retention system for a dialed fit. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1185\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8-800x1185.jpeg\" alt=\"Mavic Deemax helmet with MIPS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8-800x1185.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8-203x300.jpeg 203w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8-81x120.jpeg 81w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8-768x1138.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips8.jpeg 864w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A Fidlock magnetic buckle, Coolmax padding, mesh bug screens, and an eyewear tunnel complete the Deemax MIPS. Offered in three colors and S, M, and L sizing, the helmet sells for $156. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"781\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1-800x781.jpeg\" alt=\"Mavic Deemax helmet with MIPS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1-800x781.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1-297x290.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1-120x117.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1-768x749.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips1.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"776\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6-800x776.jpeg\" alt=\"Mavic Deemax helmet with MIPS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6-800x776.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6-297x288.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6-120x116.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6-768x745.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Mavic-Deemax-helmet-mips6.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Highlights</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>• Integrated Mips technology</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Autofit strap system</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• new Ergo Hold SL + 3-position Retention System</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Eyewear Tunnel / Google compatible</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Coolmax® padding</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>WEIGHT: 390g (M)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>COLORS: White, Black, Military Green</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SIZE RANGE: S, M, L</li>\n\n\n\n<li>MSRP: $156.00 USD</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-deemax-helmet-mips/\">Mavic Deemax Helmet Doesn’t Come in Yellow, Unless You Count the MIPS Liner</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"338f4cce30a4808e5ee0ed85343e5fbd32de192ffc4888fb192b0393bf7b2623","category":"Cycling"}